    "offset": 113072,
    "slot_size": 214,
    "data_size": 210,
    "nom_orig": "Maya",
    "texte_orig": "But[SP]I[SP]can't[SP]lose[SP]now![SP]I'm[SP]not[SP]just[SP]facing\nKing[SP]Leo,[SP]after[SP]all.[SP]I'm[SP]up[SP]against[SP]myself,\nas[SP]well!",
